cosmic-ext-flux (3.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Optionally pause playback while on battery power (issue #1): an opt-in
    toggle in the applet, off by default. The daemon reads the on-battery
    state from UPower on the system bus and pauses/resumes accordingly,
    degrading gracefully where UPower is unavailable.
  * Fix the applet crashing when its popup is opened: the added settings row
    pushed the popup past its height limit, tripping an xdg_surface protocol
    error. The popup height ceiling was raised so all rows fit.

 -- Franz <cosmic-flux-info@franz-net.dev>  Fri, 26 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0000

cosmic-ext-flux (3.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Automatically pause playback when an app is fullscreen (issue #13):
    the wallpaper is hidden anyway, so the daemon stops decoding and drops
    to ~0% CPU, resuming when you leave fullscreen. On by default; toggle
    in the applet.
  * Optional "also pause when maximized" toggle in the applet (off by
    default). A manual pause always takes precedence over auto-resume.
  * Daemon logs to the systemd journal at info level by default; RUST_LOG
    still overrides.

 -- Franz <cosmic-flux-info@franz-net.dev>  Thu, 25 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0000

cosmic-ext-flux (2.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix postinst systemd handoff under sudo: use systemctl --global enable
    plus a runuser-based immediate stop/start of the user units, instead of
    su without the user's session bus.

 -- Franz <cosmic-flux-info@franz-net.dev>  Tue, 09 Jun 2026 23:50:00 +0000

cosmic-ext-flux (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rename project to cosmic-ext-flux per the COSMIC trademark policy.
  * New App ID and D-Bus name: io.github.franz_net.* (was com.system76.*).
  * Migrate user config and frame cache from the old App ID automatically.
  * Conflicts/Replaces/Provides cosmic-flux for a clean upgrade path.

 -- Franz <cosmic-flux-info@franz-net.dev>  Tue, 09 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0000

